    {
      "offset": "0x63540",
      "back_en": "Ho, Master Haku. What brings you here?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'seek' (procuras) virou 'te traz' (brings); sentido levemente alterado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63619",
      "back_en": "Verily. 'Tis my first journey in company",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel; 'sojourn' como jornada aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63649",
      "back_en": "of such great number, to be sure!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Continuação correta."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6368b",
      "back_en": "Me? Ah, by the heavens! Duty compels the faithful",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'What, I?'→'Eu?' e 'steadfast'→'fiel' aceitáveis."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x636be",
      "back_en": "Maroro to assist the sweet Lady Rulutieh.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel ao sentido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63755",
      "back_en": "Mistress Rulutieh, you need not search any longer",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "OK; 'Mistress' mantido em inglês."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63788",
      "back_en": "for the table-salt! I myself found it.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'the thing itself'→'o' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63ed0",
      "back_en": "Ah, but to dine on such delicacies made by",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'sup upon victuals' bem traduzido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x63f05",
      "back_en": "Lady Rulutieh's own hand! How hungry I am!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x65680",
      "back_en": "'There's nothing to worry about' is what they",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x656b5",
      "back_en": "told me just before the disastrous gigiri hunt.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel ao sentido."
    }
